   Methods: We searched PubMed for prospective trials evaluating psychosocial predictors for weight loss with RYGBS published between 2000 and 2010. Manual searches of references listed in review articles, case series and anecdotal reports supplemented our literature search. Additional literature on post-bariatric surgery psychosocial outcomes and management of psychiatric sequelae in bariatric surgery patients are discussed in this review.
